Package lazyTrees

Class LazySearchTree<E extends java.lang.Comparable<? super E>>

java.lang.Object
lazyTrees.LazySearchTree<E>
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable
public class LazySearchTree<E extends java.lang.Comparable<? super E>>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
This class contains the BST with an inner Node class. Different methods help modify the generic BST such as insert, remove, or softly delete.
